  </p>
  <br>
  <h2>With Level App you can:</h2>
  <ul id="selling-points" class="mbl">
    <li>Explore an up-to-date trick list in our database<!--tricktionary--></li>
    <li>Create your own tricks or combos<!--, and share them with your friends--></li>
    <li>Generate random combos</li>
    <!--li>
        Generate combos for specific tricking styles with many parameters,<br>
        like combo length, tricks involved, and many more
    </li>
    <li>
        Easily organize all the above into lists.<br>
        Defaults include "favorites", "next sampler goals", and "experimental".
    </li>
    <li>
      Easily mark the tricks you can do as "landed" so that you can use them in your combos
    </li>
    <li>Set goals and watch yourself progress over time</li-->
  </ul>
  <br>
  <% if !tricker_signed_in? %>
    <h2>What are you waiting for?</h2>
    <p><%= link_to "Join the community today!", new_tricker_registration_path, :class => "btn btn-blue mrs" %></p>
    <br>
  <% end %>
</div>

